SUMMARY CHECKLIST FOR FUTURE APPS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
[ ] 1. Check `vite.config.ts` - Remove `basename`.
[ ] 2. Create `auth.login.tsx` and map `auth.path` in `shopify.server.ts`.
[ ] 3. Update `Session` model in `schema.prisma`.
[ ] 4. Inject `npx prisma db push --accept-data-loss` into `netlify.toml`.
[ ] 5. Isolate Tailwind CSS from Polaris routes.
[ ] 6. (Optional) Inject any missing `.env` variables (e.g., GEMINI_API_KEY) into Netlify Dashboard matching the code.

Following this exact procedure will resurrect any scavenged app in this monorepo to a production-ready, installable state.
